    "body": "It appears that although the [Dockerfile](https://github.com/sigp/lighthouse/blob/stable/lcli/Dockerfile#L7) has the arg `PORTABLE` [which is set](https://github.com/sigp/lighthouse/blob/stable/.github/workflows/docker.yml#L145) `=true` in the build script, `PORTABLE` doesn't actually do anything:\r\n\r\n```\r\n$ grep -R PORTABLE .\r\n./.github/workflows/docker.yml:                      --build-arg PORTABLE=true \\\r\n./lcli/Dockerfile:ARG PORTABLE\r\n./lcli/Dockerfile:ENV PORTABLE $PORTABLE\r\n```",
